Author: Mmaarten
Name: &b&lThe Great War
Description: It all comes down to this. Now is your time to shine!

Dialog.&e&lAstrid: Are you ready [PLAYER]? I have a plan. Meet me in the Shrine for Kyurem in Northrun!

Objective: Head to Northrun and enter the Shrine for Kyurem

Dialog.[PLAYER]: &oIf there was ever a Shrine in Northrun... this was it.
&oSo in here, &3Kyurem&r&o should be in a deep slumber...

Objective: Follow the path to the top

Dialog.[PLAYER]: &oSeems like nobody has walked this path in a long time.
&oHmm, this is quite a hike, I should have brought something to drink.
&oHmmm, This used to be a door I think...
&oSeems like it is frozen in place. Maybe I can climb through it though.

Objective: Navigate through the maze of ice

Dialog.[PLAYER]: &oMy hands are freezing, If only I had some Hot chocolate...
&oHmm... This seems like another maze... But what is that?
&oLooks like this is a timed one. I have only 60 seconds to complete this...

Objective: Beat the second maze in less than 60 seconds

NewDialog.&7&lMaze: Looks like you did not make it in time...
Hmm... I'll let you go this time...

NewDialog.[PLAYER]: &3&oKyurem&r &ois waiting for me, I better hurry.
&oHmm, looks like this is the final maze before I am at &3&oKyurem&r&o's Masterball.
&oThere is an inscription on the wall here...
&oNot everything is as it seems... What could that mean?

Objective: Navigate through the maze of illusions

NewDialog.[PLAYER]: &oNow I get why no soul has ever tried to wake up &3&oKyurem&r&o!
&oI feel like I am close though. This bridge looks too majestic.

Dialog.&e&lAstrid: You may not be the recognized Zeinova Champion, but you are &6Sophro's&r Champion!
Take the Master Ball from the stand! We've got a plan.
We will replace it with a dummy Master Ball!
Perfect! Now we'll just put this fake Master Ball in it's place!
Now, let's get out of here! There's a path leading out of here to the right of the ice mazes. I'll meet you there.

Objective: Follow the path out of the Shrine (There's a hidden path to the right of the ice mazes)

NewDialog.&e&lAstrid: Why is there so much activity at the shrine entrance?

Dialog.&e&lAstrid: [PLAYER]... I think the Great War has begun...
Dialog.[PLAYER]: I don't see Danielle or Vidar anywhere...
Dialog.&e&lAstrid: They're probably inside the shrine already...
... I sense something going on...
Yes... The Pokmon have arrived to help us win...
We will overpower those Statera members!

AutoBattleNpc.&3&lStatera Member: Look who it is! The traitor! You could never beat me!
You're a lot stronger than you look...
Ha ha! And they told me &oyou&r had a strong &dAura&r!
I don't understand how you could leave Statera! Our strength is far greater than Sophro's!
I- I guess I underestimated you...
What did I just tell you!
This war will be won by Statera! Sophro will lose!
There's no way for you to win! Give up!

Dialog.&e&lAstrid: It seems they've found our dummy Master Ball! Go finish this war [PLAYER]!

AutoBattleNpc.&8&lVidar: Aw look who it is... Why hello [PLAYER]! Or should I call you Weakling, because you'll never beat me!
My dream will be realized, and you will regret this.
The real Champion of Zeinova will be victorious!
That's what happens when you betray others...

Dialog.&d&lDanielle: I will be superior... I am superior.

Dialog.&e&lAstrid: Spike!
[PLAYER]! Your &dAura&r just spiked!
This is wonderful!
&3Kyurem&r and the Swords of Justice are lending you their strength!

AutoBattleNpc.&d&lDanielle: This War will be won by Statera!
Why... Why do you always end up being the Hero?!

Dialog.&8&lVidar: You may have won but this is not the last you will see of me!
I will be back! Come on Statera Members! Let's get out of here!

Dialog.&e&lAstrid: Looks like one of the Swords of Justice wants to join you on your journey, [PLAYER].
You bonded quite a bit during the battle.
I'm sure you'll learn a lot from the Swords of Justice.
I cannot say what will become of &3Statera&r at this time... but I can tell you this is not over.

We will work hard to gain back the region's trust, &3Statera&r has painted us in an awful light, and we must be able to shoulder this burden of being painted as the Bad Guys, while we rebuild Zeinova.
Thank you [PLAYER], this never would have been possible without you.
Your bond with your team, our team, and &3Kyurem&r saved me, our tribe, our region, and potentially the world.

Objective: Type /accept to accept Professor Hemlock's call

Dialog.&c&lProfessor Hemlock: Hey, [PLAYER]? Can you come by the lab? We need to talk...

Objective: Visit Professor Hemlock at his lab

Dialog.&c&lProfessor Hemlock: [PLAYER]... youve gone through a lot of heartache because of me
My research gave &3Stratera&r the chance to advance and begin this terrible war
I received an alert from &3Strateras&r A.I H.A.P.P.Y. It appears &8Vidar&r has been arrested due to the research he funded.
I will be taking some time off from research, so that I may become connected with reality once more.
Science and research has blinded me, and Id like to become more connected with my Pokemon again, like in the past.
It appears my journey here in Zeinova is over however yours is only just beginning, [PLAYER]. Your name will forever be etched in the history of these islands, just like their Storybook tales
Do us proud, [PLAYER]. &dDanielle&r and I will be rooting for you, even if she doesnt realize it yet.
